{"tid":1091692,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Konami營收增至17.5億美元，多虧了手遊和電競","createTime":"2019-04-04T09:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T05:58:17.000Z","uid":100680,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8a3d3a9909fd1d28f1f14ea7f62e5dd65329cd97","tid":1091692,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T09:46:46.000Z","msg":"對很多玩家來說，Konami現在可能不再是他們關注的對象了，這個曾經象徵品質的遊戲大廠，突然之間從神壇跌到眾人唾罵的境地。然而Konami公司的收入卻不跌反升。儘管只有少數的大作，但根據他們最近的財報，Konami的營收令人驚訝，達到了17.5億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.playgame.wiki/2019/04/03/a826b229ff/64a05d19b39295237d399c7fb3039368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.playgame.wiki%2F2019%2F04%2F03%2Fa826b229ff%2F64a05d19b39295237d399c7fb3039368.jpg&h=a5f5fcc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據財報顯示，Koanm 2018年營收相比往年同比增長7.8%，營業利潤達到了3.89億美元，同比增長2.4%。那麽到底是什麽讓很少開發3A遊戲的Konami賺了這麽多錢?<br />\n<br />\nKonami表示，這主要感謝公司的手遊和電競項目，此外還有《實況足球》的MyClub模式。Konami的遊戲部門過去一年創收9.63億美元。而柏青哥遊戲機（日本賭博遊戲機）部門創收1.65億美元，同比下滑8.2%。<br />\n<br />\n簡單來說，Konami多點開花的生意模式似乎很有效果。儘管他們可能不在開發一個3A級《潛龍諜影》或《惡魔城》遊戲，但Konami的日子活得還是很滋潤的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://playgame.wiki/news/a826b229ff\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplaygame.wiki%2Fnews%2Fa826b229ff&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=d16a1214\" target=\"_blank\">https://playgame.wiki/news/a826b229ff</a>"},{"pid":"e59c370360056237e8f5210ba99375b8b918a4a2","tid":1091692,"uid":3419,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T09:48:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母垃撚圾<br />\n玩佢啲手機game嘅都係"},{"pid":"2ca324268cf71e2dcb1b4e121c1253a1600aa17c","tid":1091692,"uid":55468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T09:51:34.000Z","msg":"Winning隻手機版真係差唔多養晒成間K廠咁濟.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3f66fefc3387fb09b2846f948e53d493eb191c","tid":1091692,"uid":46511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T10:41:15.000Z","msg":"不務正業<br />\n搞死Slient Hill系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28aad01fb0a05a5f6c6c64f4cfbd3e28c2fee107","tid":1091692,"uid":33357,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n搞死metal gear, silent hill, 無尊重過小島仲要追擊"},{"pid":"e0564152e947e63a111d5fa97a665888e2491c31","tid":1091692,"uid":179967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:38:41.000Z","msg":"你有你屌 佢有佢繼續出手機驚cap水"},{"pid":"79df2be1fc8b88b1e150ddf1a0c4067a5e7368b4","tid":1091692,"uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:39:52.000Z","msg":"音驚清泉"},{"pid":"aa377f8db23675edb23b2906bf416aed2b23f077","tid":1091692,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:41:15.000Z","msg":"食屎啦Konami"},{"pid":"7e8a4930dbf72b6d1cad12306d7d2767478198ff","tid":1091692,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"越反越賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4079098a311f273aaf9834533f975ee05582fb","tid":1091692,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e8a4930dbf72b6d1cad12306d7d2767478198ff","tid":1091692,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"越反越賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T14:53:21.000Z","msg":"全世界都走向低質"},{"pid":"ad8764b6ffe0bca3dc40426e521b179b96834591","tid":1091692,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7e8a4930dbf72b6d1cad12306d7d2767478198ff","tid":1091692,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"越反越賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h